PHPIDS plugin for CakePHP 1.3
------------------------------

INSTALLATION
------------------------------
1. Copy phpids plugin folder into your Cakephp plugins folder (app/plugins/)
2. Configure your PHPIDS settings (phpids/config/phpids.php)
3. Set base path in PHPIDS configuration file (phpids/vendors/phpids/IDS/config/Config.ini.php)
4. Add 

$this->requestAction("/phpids/phpids_intrusions/detect");

to the actions you wish the IDS to monitor



